name: Magislayer Strategist - Nobunaga Oda
effect:
2 "Magislayer" Monsters
This card only be Link Summoned OR Special Summoned by an "Magislay" or "Magikill" card effect, and can't be Summoned by other ways. You can only Special Summon 1 "Magislayer Strategist - Nobunaga Oda" per turn. You can Special Summon this card from your Extra Deck by sending 2 Spell/Traps you control to the GY. If this card is Special Summoned, you can send 1 "Magislay" or "Magikill" Spell/Trap from your Deck to your GY: Draw 1 card, and if you do, set 1 "Magislay" or "Magikill" Spell/Trap from your Deck to your Spell/Traps Zone with a different name of the card send to the GY for activating this effect. (Quick Effect): You can return this card you control to the Extra Deck and if you do, you can Special Summon 1 non-Link "Magislayer" Monster from your Extra Deck. You can only activate this effect of "Magislayer Strategist - Nobunaga Oda" once per turn.
